These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, juice, sprite, iced-tea
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: metal, r&b, salsa, techno
There are 4 different nationalities: canadian, colombian, indonesian, polish
The people have 4 different hobbies: chess, baking, sudoku, dancing
1. the colombian is the fan of techno##1
2. the indonesian is between the person drinking sprite and the person drinking iced-tea##2
3. the colombian is the person who's hobby is chess##1
4. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the left of the person who's hobby is chess##1
5. the fan of metal is on the left of the canadian##1
6. the person who's hobby is sudoku is the person drinking sprite##1
7. the fan of r&b is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
8. the canadian is on the far right##1
9. the person drinking juice is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Beverage   | juice | iced-tea   | 7up  | sprite  |
| Music-Genre   | r&b    | techno    | metal      | salsa    |
| Nationality   | polish | colombian | indonesian | canadian |
| Hobby     | dancing  | chess       | baking    | sudoku     |

