.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-2::.
City: paris, nizza, liverpool, hannover
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, adventure, scientific, western
4 different pets are kept: bird, dog, frog, lizard
The people have 4 different jobs:  manager, firefighter, engineer, coach
1. the coach is on the right of the person traveling to hannover##1
2. the person traveling to paris is on the far right##1
3. the owner of the lizard is the firefighter##1
4. the person traveling to liverpool is on the right of the person traveling to nizza##1
5. the person watching western movies is between the owner of the frog and the manager##2
6. the coach is between the person watching western movies and the owner of the lizard##2
7. the owner of the bird is on the far right##1
8. the person watching adventure movies is on the left of the person traveling to liverpool##1
9. the person watching scientific movies is on the right of the owner of the dog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4      |
| City         | hannover | nizza    | liverpool  | paris    |
| Movie-Genre   | action      | adventure  | western  | scientific |
| Pet           | lizard      | frog       | dog      | bird       |
| Job         | firefighter    | coach | engineer | manager |

