The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, fishing, photography, traveling
The people have 4 different jobs:  analyst, lawyer, paramedic, pilot
4 different pets are kept: bird, hamster, lizard, goat
1. the paramedic is the owner of the hamster##1
2. the owner of the hamster is on the left of the pilot##1
3. the owner of the lizard is on the left of the owner of the hamster##1
4. the owner of the hamster is on the left of the owner of the bird##1
5. the farmhouse house is on the left of the person who's hobby is photography##1
6. the lawyer is the person who's hobby is traveling##1
7. the art-deco house is on the right of the person who's hobby is photography##1
8. the gothic-revival house is between the person who's hobby is camping and the person who's hobby is traveling##2
9. the person who's hobby is photography is between the farmhouse house and the lawyer##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2     |      3      |     4     |
| House        | cottage | farmhouse     | gothic-revival   | art-deco     |
| Hobby       | fishing   | camping   | photography | traveling |
| Job         | analyst   | paramedic | pilot       | lawyer    |
| Pet   | lizard    | hamster | bird  | goat    |

