The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, epic, romance, scientific
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: amaryllis, daisy, aconite, balloon-flower
 1. the person eating lemon is on the right of the person eating garlic##1
 2. the person who growsamaryllis is on the far left##1
 3. the cape-cod house is the person eating garlic##1
 4. the cape-cod house is on the left of the person who growsaconite##1
 5. the person watching scientific movies is on the left of the person eating peach##1
 6. the person eating lemon is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1
 7. the colonial house is on the left of the person eating asparagus##1
 8. the cottage house is the person watching epic movies##1
 9. the person eating lemon is between the person who growsballoon-flower and the person watching adventure movies##2
10. the person watching romance movies is the person who growsaconite##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |       2       |       3       |     4      |
