 1. the person who's birthday is in september is on the right of the fan of blues##1
 2. the person watching fantasy movies is the vegafina-smoker##1
 3. the fan of dubstep is between the vegafina-smoker and the person who's birthday is in april##2
 4. the fan of metal is the person who's birthday is in september##1
 5. the blend-smoker is on the left of the person watching zombie movies##1
 6. the person watching fantasy movies is on the left of the person who's birthday is in august##1
 7. the bongani-smoker is the person who's birthday is in november##1
 8. the fan of soul is on the far right##1
 9. the person watching fantasy movies is on the right of the person watching time-travel movies##1
10. the vegafina-smoker is the person who's birthday is in september##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel | fantasy | family  | zombie  |
| Music-Genre   | blues       | metal   | dubstep | soul    |
| Cigar   | bongani   | vegafina   | blend | oliveros |
