 4. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the right of the person traveling to liverpool##1
 5. the fan of metal is the person traveling to berlin##1
 6. the fan of indie is on the far left##1
 7. the person driving the boat is on the left of the person driving the tram##1
 8. the fan of house is on the far right##1
 9. the person driving the roller is between the person driving the snowmobile and the person who's sport is cycling##2
10. the person traveling to liverpool is on the left of the person traveling to san-francisco##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |     3      |     4     |
