 6. the person who likes aquamarine is on the right of the person eating corn##1
 7. the owner of the rat is on the left of the electrician##1
 8. the owner of the turtle is between the person eating corn and the person eating onion##2
 9. the person eating plum is on the right of the owner of the horse##1
10. the person who likes aquamarine is between the person eating corn and the person eating onion##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |     2      |      3      |       4       |
| Job   | dancer    | police-officer    | musician      | electrician |
| Food       | corn        | plum       | onion       | nectarine     |
| Color      | yellow | aquamarine | apricot | azure        |
